PrecisTransfer to Sotelmont Inc., by quit-claim letters patent or such other appropriate instrument, of certain commercial rights acquired by the Crown upon the dissolution of 121328 Canada Limitée et al. (Château Mont Sainte-Anne Holdings Inc.) pursuant to the Canada Business Corporations Act (s.221), more particularly, the rights to operate various refreshment stalls or amusement concessions at Mont Sainte-Anne Park, a ski resort situated near Sainte-Anne-de-Beaupre, Quebec.
